data.title: Wendy Sharpe
data.content:
As Artist in Residence  for the State Library of NSW here is a pic for their  faces  of NSW  project  to be shown later this year .  Join me  take a selfie  it could be part of the exhibition  at the library ( if you are in NSW)and  tag it as. #NewSelfWales
